div.p: Object Space Local model coordinates (chair's own "up/forward")
World Space Shared studio coordinates (common floor/walls/lighting)
Camera Space Camera's viewfinder perspective (forward = toward subject)
Clip Space Homogeneous coordinates (w-component for perspective)
Screen Space Final 2D pixel positions (ready for rasterization)

ul.li: 4D vectors (x, y, z, w) for 3D points
Like accounting for perspective effects in photography
